==Sliced Bread==

Sliced Bread - Officially the lamest thing since sliced bread.

==Why?==

It is a form of fascism. Who gets to choose how bread is sliced? What if we do not want to eat bread sliced vertically along the loaf? Surely it is better to sell bread un-sliced so people can express their creativity through which way they wish to slice it.


